## Local development

```bash
# Start Expo (QR + web preview)
yarn dev

# Open web in the browser after starting
# In Expo dev UI, press "w" or open the Web platform
```

## Linting

```bash
# Run lint
yarn expo lint || yarn lint
```

## Build (web static export)

```bash
# Export web build to dist/
yarn build:web
```

## Useful notes

- Environment: Expo SDK 54, React Native 0.81, TypeScript ~5.9, strict mode.
- Path alias: import using `@/` (e.g., `import { Foo } from '@/components/ui/Foo'`).
- Router: Use `expo-router` APIs (`Link`, `useRouter`, `useLocalSearchParams`).
- UI primitives: check `components/ui/*` before building new components.
